item.title: NIN - “The Hand that Feeds” remixes
item.dc:creator: Brian Kirsten
item.content:encoded: Fan remixes of NIN's "The Hand that Feeds". But here's the kicker....The Ghostbusters theme + NIN = Friggen Joy! (that's my second post with friggen in it...must be my word of the day). Nathan Chase's "The Ghost that Feeds" (Links courtesy of Waxy)
